stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Inactive

    note right of Inactive
        Pac-Man has no rich FSM. Behaviour is driven by
        ResetState() / DeathSequence() toggling the
        component, renderer, collider and Movement.
        Eating power pellets affects ghosts, not Pac-Man's state.
    end note

    Inactive --> Active : ResetState() (NewRound / respawn)

    state Active {
        [*] --> Controlled
        Controlled --> Controlled : HandleInput (WASD/arrows) -> Movement.SetDirection
        Controlled --> Controlled : UpdateRotation toward direction
        AI --> AI : PacmanAgent.OnActionReceived -> SetDirection
        Controlled --> AI : aiControlled = true (autopilot/training)
        AI --> Controlled : aiControlled = false
    }

    Active --> Dead : Ghost collision (not frightened) -> PacmanEaten -> DeathSequence
    Dead --> Active : lives>0, Invoke ResetState after 3s
    Dead --> [*] : lives==0, GameOver
